---
description: React Native engineering rules for maintainable screens, navigation, shared modules, and hybrid mobile features.
globs:
  - "**/*.tsx"
  - "**/*.ts"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use this rule when working on React Native application code.
- Clarify Expo vs bare RN vs hybrid architecture first.
- Keep `screen`, `components`, `hooks`, `store`, `service`, and `bridge` responsibilities separate.
- Do not place complete business orchestration, API calls, and navigation logic inside a single screen file.
